Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.input.database

Interface Summary
IAuthenticationSource All sources of authentication must implement this interface.
IStarNameAndAUIDSource This interface must be implemented by any class wishing to retrieve star name or AUID from a database.
 

Class Summary
AAVSOAuthenticationSource This class authenticates with respect to an AAVSO source.
AAVSODatabaseConnector This class handles the details of connecting to the MySQL AAVSO observation database, a data accessor.
AAVSODatabaseObservationReader This class reads variable star observations from an AAVSO database and yields a collection of observations for one star.
AIDStarNameAndAUIDSource Deprecated. Use VSXStarNameAndAUIDSource instead.
AuthenticationTask This concurrent task attempts to authenticate against one or more authentication sources, completing when one is successful or all are exhausted.
Authenticator This class is responsible for authenticating against one or more authentication sources, caching results such as whether authentication has happened, user name, observer code.
CitizenSkyAuthenticationSource This class authenticates with respect to a Citizen Sky source.
VSXStarNameAndAUIDSource This class obtains star name and AUID information from the VSX database.
 

Enum Summary
DatabaseType The type of database to be connected to.
